    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in pristine shape, inside and out, and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, so it's ready for its next adventure with zero work needed. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
