    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The M-Double Clutch Transmission (DCT) provides lightning-fast shifts, complemented by a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) offering precise damping adjustments. With flawless paint depth and a showroom-spec interior, this is a turnkey example for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak BMW M engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
