    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, mirror-like exterior finish completely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the original trim is flawless. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard with a full, documented service history, ensuring a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality masterpiece that satisfies even the most discerning collector's eye.",
      "price": 48500.0,
