    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a legacy of meticulous care. Every component functions with factory-grade precision, offering the discerning enthusiast an unparalleled driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such distinguished caliber and aesthetic integrity.",
